subproject.description: The objective this IP is to lay the framework for the institutional development of the newly established Regional Planning Commission (RPC) under the auspices of the Office of the Prime Ministry.  The main outputs of the project is to design and propose an administrative and organizational structure for the Regional Planning Commission as per its mandate (Law No 26/2010) as well as develop a full-fledged Project Document to operationalize the organizational structure recommended by the IP Team
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: STRUCTURE & FUNCTION OF RPC DE

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
